@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy 🐾";
}

<div class="container py-4">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <h1 class="fw-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy 🐾</h1>
            <p class="lead text-muted mb-5">We take your privacy as seriously as a cat takes its nap time. 😴</p>

            <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="h4 text-primary">Cookies 🍪</h2>
                    <p>We use cookies only when strictly necessary. Not the delicious tuna ones, but the boring digital kind. We promise not to track your paw prints across the internet unless you explicitly ask us to (which would be weird).</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="h4 text-primary"> Data Collection 🕵️‍♂️</h2>
                    <p>We collect very little data. Specifically:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Your amazing blog posts (obviously).</li>
                        <li>The time you posted them (so we know if you're a night owl or an early bird).</li>
                        <li>Absolutely zero information about your dog. We don't talk about dogs here. 🐶🚫</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="h4 text-primary"> Third Parties 🤝</h2>
                    <p>We do not sell, trade, or transfer your data to outside parties. Unless they offer us premium catnip. Just kidding. (Maybe.)</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="alert alert-info text-center mt-5" role="alert">
                <strong>Questions?</strong> Meow at us at <a href="mailto:privacy@purrfectblog.com" class="alert-link">privacy@purrfectblog.com</a>.
            </div>
            
            <p class="text-center text-muted mt-4 small">
                <em>Last updated: When the cat decided to walk across the keyboard.</em>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>